OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782755283
OL,3,CReform UK announces Greater Manchester
OL,4,Cmayoral candidate
OL,6,FReform UK has announced Sian Astley as
OL,7,Fthe party's candidate for the Greater
OL,8,FManchester mayoral by-election,
OL,9,Ftriggered by the election of Andy
OL,10,FBurnham as MP.
OL,12,FA graduate of Manchester University,
OL,13,FMs Astley currently lives in
OL,14,FFallowfield, in Manchester, where she
OL,15,Fruns a design and property business.
OL,17,FIn the recent May elections, she was
OL,18,Felected Reform UK councillor for
OL,19,FBaguley, Wythenshawe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
