OL,3,CReform UK announces Greater Manchester
OL,4,Cmayoral candidate
OL,6,FShe is also the party's leader on
OL,7,FManchester City Council.
OL,9,FShe said: "I am delighted to be chosen
OL,10,Fas Reform UK's candidate for Mayor
OL,11,FGreater Manchester - I am determined
OL,12,Fto improve communities and the lives
OL,13,Fof working people.
OL,15,F"Over the years, we have all seen our
OL,16,Ftowns and areas across Greater
OL,17,FManchester decline, with high streets
OL,18,Fleft unattended, unfunded and unloved.
OL,19,FThey need to be placed front and
OL,20,Fcentre again.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782755283
OL,3,CReform UK announces Greater Manchester
OL,4,Cmayoral candidate
OL,6,F"One of my first acts as Mayor will be
OL,7,Fto open up the books on contracts Andy
OL,8,FBurnham awarded during his time as
OL,9,FLabour's Mayor, at least one of which
OL,10,Fwas to a company which made
OL,11,Fsubstantial donations to his Mayoral
OL,12,Fcampaign.
OL,14,F"Politics needs real people with real
OL,15,Flife experience. People like me."
OL,17,FThe by-election is scheduled to take
OL,18,Fplace on 30 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
